txt.en: You have entered a Housing Neighbourhood. The houses here can be (or already have been) purchased by players or kinships.\n\nThis neighbourhood has vendors offering various wares--including items to decorate a house--as well as a Vault-keeper. If you own a house in this neighbourhood, you will receive a discount from the vendors there.
